Ok after you paste that into your compile file WHILE EDITING IT click save. After you do that just double click on compile. Press “c” then press enter and wait for it to compile your server. After it is compiled, press any key, then press “r” and then press enter. Wait for a few seconds to make sure no errors come up and your server should be online. Then just open up your moparscape client, put in your name and pass, and have fun :D, please lemme know if I helped any. Anymore questions ask emm and I will do my best to help.
